{
  "stem": "22174.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When-- after Hitler came to power, all the teachers had to-- had to adjust their teaching to the Nazi policies.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we had a teacher in German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he gave a-- he-- he-- and he was a-- he was a Democrat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But he had to do-- in order to keep his job, he had to do what he was told.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he once gave the class [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a topic for an essay.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember exactly the-- the theme.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- it was a [? theme ?] about nationalism, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And more Nazism and so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But for the Jews-- for the Jewish kids-- and, incidentally, at that year, all the Jewish kids were in one class.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For us, he gave us different-- a different topic so we didn't have to-- we wouldn't have to write about that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but I took the theme-- the other theme about nationalism, but I turned it around, and I wrote about Zionism, because Zionism is Jewish-- Jewish nationalism, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I turned it around and wrote about Zionism as nationalism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I, I think I also got an E on that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think I also got an Excellent, an E, an E on that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I always had to-- had to do things the opposite that-- than, than I was expected to.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It didn't make life easier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What are your memories of your father?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was always very critical of me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whatever I did, criticized it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it had an effect on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I developed an inferiority complex.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] But I don't want to, to talk more, more about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have a sister, who, who lives in California.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Johanna.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
